1
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:36,799
The last spot

2
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:41,439
The real show is about to begin

3
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,280
The top three have arrived

4
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:57,079
Only one spot remains

5
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,280
Everyone, hang in there

6
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,240
We're almost there

7
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,960
They're catching up

8
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,000
I can't carry you any longer

9
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:26,039
There's only one spot left

10
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:26,759
You go first

11
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:27,960
Qingxue

12
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,360
They haven't recovered yet

13
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,560
They can't move that fast

14
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,039
I'll help them up slowly

15
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,080
Can you manage on your own?

16
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,840
I'm not a porcelain doll

17
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,840
How do you think Green Wood Hall

18
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,520
fought its way up all these years?

19
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,120
Wait for me here

20
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:42,360
I'll come back for you after I win

21
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,080
Okay?

22
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:53,120
I can't count on that last spot

23
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,919
Hurry, go

24
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:54,520
Qingxue

25
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,479
We promised to reach the finish together.

26
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:58,120
Enough talk.

27
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,840
Only by passing the Path of Healing

28
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,919
can we keep Green Wood Hall's Medicine Master seat.

29
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,599
Help!

30
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:15,599
She's not going to make it.

31
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:32,599
You have passed the Xuanshui Hall trial.

32
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:35,400
By the rules, you must swear before the Medicine Sovereign

33
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,520
and receive the bestowed seal

34
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,759
to become an official apothecary.

35
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:40,719
The free-spirited wanderer's Path of Healing:

36
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:43,159
Doing good deeds without leaving a name,

37
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,800
Healing according to your true heart,

38
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,560
And coveting neither fame nor fortune.

39
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,759
Are you willing to uphold this path?

40
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,159
Go!

41
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,800
Yang Yunfan, you can do it!

42
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,759
Someone's coming.

43
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,199
Fourth place

44
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,519
Ge Tianyu of Liujin Hall

45
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,920
Just as I thought.

46
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:19,439
A paper tiger can only bark.

47
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:25,360
Deputy Medicine Master Song,

48
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,399
Hurry up and announce the results.

49
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,439
I'm getting tired.

50
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,600
What's with this big show?

51
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,480
This is an assessment.

52
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,480
You've really gone above and beyond.

53
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,920
Bringing along a whole entourage.

54
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,600
Shouldn't we give you a Best Compassion Award?

55
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,839
If you don't show off at the finish line,

56
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,800
it really wouldn't reflect

57
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,319
that chivalrous heart of yours, right?

58
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,120
I'd like to keep a low profile too.

59
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,879
But who told you to set up the finish line

60
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:37,959
like it's some kind of fashion show?

61
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,959
Without bringing some people along,

62
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:41,360
how could I walk the red carpet?

63
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,639
Yang Yunfan,

64
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:45,399
is something wrong with your head?

65
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:47,920
Take a good look, please.

66
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,720
The slots are already filled.

67
00:06:51,279 --> 00:06:53,319
You've been eliminated, okay?

68
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:54,800
And we wouldn't deign

69
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,040
to compete on the same stage

70
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,079
with someone as unethical as you.

71
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:01,079
Deputy Medicine Master Song,

72
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,839
hurry up and announce the results.

73
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,279
Let's see how arrogant you are then.

74
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,519
For this round of assessment,

75
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,360
first place

76
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,879
goes to Yang Yunfan.

77
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,120
Are you serious? What?

78
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:21,680
Yes!

79
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,240
We won!

80
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,120
Fantastic!

81
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,240
Second place, Ye Qingxue.

82
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:31,800
Yes!

83
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,720
Fantastic!

84
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:38,279
Isn't your big brother amazing?

85
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:39,319
You...

86
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:41,079
Third place, Li Xiangyang.

87
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,720
Fourth place, Lu Tanxiang.

88
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,800
Song Ci,

89
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:53,079
don't think being the chief examiner

90
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:54,360
means you can do whatever you want.

91
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,480
I was clearly the first to arrive.

92
00:07:57,519 --> 00:08:00,000
Striking a woman is hardly admirable.

93
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,279
Shame on you!

94
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,120
Long before this round of assessment,

95
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,439
I had already placed the hidden rule

96
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:17,160
in the presence of the notary panel,

97
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,000
inside this sealed box.

98
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,079
What hidden rule?

99
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:21,040
According to the hidden rule,

100
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,439
Yang Yunfan is in first place.

101
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,160
I'd really like to see

102
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,319
what bullshit rule this is.

103
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,160
Long before the assessment,

104
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,439
I had already stated

105
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:33,120
this round tests not only medical skill,

106
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:36,039
but also ethics and adaptability.

107
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,919
Therefore,

108
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,120
within the miasma zone,

109
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,799
I placed a large number of patients.

110
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,480
The hidden rule is:

111
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:44,639
treating patients earns time bonuses.

112
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:46,879
Based on the final order of arrival

113
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:48,679
and the number of patients treated,

114
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:50,159
we determine this round's qualifiers.

115
00:08:50,159 --> 00:08:51,720
There's such a hidden rule?

116
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,639
This was clearly a race!

117
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,960
Why throw in some bullshit bonus points?

118
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:57,000
You should be glad it's system-scored.

119
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,720
Otherwise,

120
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,879
I'd have disqualified you long ago.

121
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,200
The dignified Li family

122
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,240
actually raised such a cold-blooded Medicine Holder.

123
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,120
Everyone, we won!

124
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:07,240
Wonderful! Fantastic!

125
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,159
I humbly accept the win.

126
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,639
Li Laosan, thank goodness for you!

127
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,639
Many thanks.

128
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:12,360
What are you laughing at?

129
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:13,759
All of you, shut up!

130
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:18,639
Yang Yunfan,

131
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,559
don't think winning this match

132
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,919
means you'll have the last laugh.

133
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,440
This round

134
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:26,240
is just the Medicine Holder makeup exam

135
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:28,000
The next round

136
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,960
is the Medicine Master assessment.

137
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:32,080
You don't even qualify to advance to Medicine Master.

138
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,399
Once I become Medicine Master,

139
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,879
you

140
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:38,080
and Ye Qingxue

141
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:41,240
will still yield Green Wood Hall to me.

142
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:49,200
Medicine Masters Li and Lu have arrived.

143
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:57,960
Quite the lively scene.

144
00:09:58,279 --> 00:10:00,600
Looks like I came at just the right time.

145
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:04,039
Father.

146
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:05,679
Father.

147
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,000
Yang Yunfan,

148
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:17,240
though you've proven your Yang family lineage,

149
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:19,480
you still lack seniority,

150
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:23,200
and you've made no contribution to the Mystic Medicine Society.

151
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,679
Therefore, you cannot obtain

152
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:27,399
the qualification to compete for Medicine Master.

153
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:28,559
Please leave.

154
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,720
Please leave.

155
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,000
The Path of Healing

156
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,320
is, within our Mystic Medicine Society,

157
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,799
the grand Medicine Master exam.

158
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:50,360
The Medicine Heir may be chosen from it.

159
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:54,639
A newcomer like you simply shouldn't participate.

160
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:03,320
Who says I'm not qualified to compete?

161
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,679
Young Master,

162
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:13,120
even if you've found proof of your identity,

163
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,200
that alone

164
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,279
isn't enough to enter the final Path of Healing trial.

165
00:11:17,159 --> 00:11:18,039
What do you mean?

166
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,720
To enter the final stage of the Path of Healing,

167
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:22,759
one must at least be a Medicine Holder,

168
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:24,440
and at the Kunyuan Council,

169
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,559
must be recommended by half the Elders.

170
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:30,440
I thought once my identity was confirmed,

171
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,799
it'd be smooth sailing all the way.

172
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,200
Sister Song,

173
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,919
you didn't come just to dampen my spirits, did you?

174
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,320
You must have a plan, right?

175
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,519
Well...

176
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,279
In here,

177
00:11:47,279 --> 00:11:49,799
is a way for you to enter the final Path of Healing.

178
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,799
This...

179
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,840
Everyone should have heard of it, right?

180
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,519
"The Ancient Code of Mystic Medicine."

181
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:15,120
Among the four great families of the Society,

182
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:18,039
if any family has only one bloodline left,

183
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:20,879
they can skip straight to the final trial,

184
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:22,960
to carry on the family's medical legacy.

185
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:34,200
Oh, please.

186
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,320
Some lousy old text

187
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:37,399
won't impress anyone here.

188
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:41,080
This is the top of the four ancient texts,

189
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,720
authored by the first Medicine Sovereign.

190
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:45,519
Then again,

191
00:12:45,519 --> 00:12:47,679
as an outside opportunist,

192
00:12:47,679 --> 00:12:49,000
it's understandable you wouldn't know.

193
00:12:50,279 --> 00:12:52,879
Yang Yunfan is the sole heir of the Yang family.

194
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,559
By the rules,

195
00:12:54,559 --> 00:12:57,080
he can enter the last two rounds of the Path of Healing,

196
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,519
to vie for the roles of Medicine Master and Medicine Heir.

197
00:13:06,159 --> 00:13:07,000
Indeed.

198
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,559
Brother Ge, you're mistaken there.

199
00:13:14,159 --> 00:13:16,799
The Yangs are no longer one of the four families.

200
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:19,600
Now only my Lu family

201
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:26,240
remains as one of the four great family names in the Society.

202
00:13:26,799 --> 00:13:28,240
Medicine Master Lu is right.
